OL,3,CHistoric Tudor house to be mothballed
OL,4,Cdue to council cuts
OL,6,FHistoric site Llancaiach Fawr will be
OL,7,Fmothballed at the end of the year, the
OL,8,Fcouncil which runs it has announced.
OL,10,FCaerphilly Council's cabinet says the
OL,11,Fattraction costs #485,000 to manage a
OL,12,Fyear and it's "exploring options for
OL,13,Fthe facility to be run in a different
OL,14,Fway in the future".
OL,16,FThe local authority has said it must
OL,17,Fdeliver savings in the region of
OL,18,F#45million over the next two years to
OL,19,Fsurvive, warning there are still more
OL,20,Fdifficult decisions ahead.
