OL,3,CHistoric Tudor house to be mothballed
OL,4,Cdue to council cuts
OL,6,FThe announcement comes as Caerphilly
OL,7,FCouncil had also proposed to cut its
OL,8,Fmeal delivery service in a bid to save
OL,9,F#444,000 per year. However its cabinet
OL,10,Fhas now opted to continue the service.
OL,12,FThe meals on wheels service delivers
OL,13,Faround 125,000 meals a year to around
OL,14,F320 people, and is supported by a
OL,15,Fworkforce of more than 30 caterers,
OL,16,Fdrivers and helpers.
