OL,6,FA council statement said: "The
OL,7,Fcouncil's cabinet met this week to
OL,8,Fconsider the feedback and agreed to
OL,9,Fcontinue providing the service, while
OL,10,Fdeveloping a range of further options
OL,11,Fto make the delivery of Meals Direct
OL,12,Fsustainable over the long-term."
OL,14,FCllr Morgan added: "I'm sure residents
OL,15,Fand service users will welcome this
OL,16,Fdecision, which clearly shows we have
OL,17,Flistened to the feedback from the
OL,18,Fcommunity and responded accordingly.
