OL,6,F"We will now work closely with the
OL,7,FMeals Direct team to review and
OL,8,Freconfigure the service in future, so
OL,9,Fthat it does not require the current
OL,10,Fhigh level of subsidy. We will, of
OL,11,Fcourse, keep service users informed
OL,12,Fand updated throughout this process."
OL,14,F"Whilst many will welcome this news,
OL,15,Fit is important to note that we still
OL,16,Fhave an unprecedented savings target
OL,17,Fto meet and we will now have to
OL,18,Fconsider other options to deliver
OL,19,Fsavings. Unfortunately, there are
OL,20,Fstill further difficult decisions
OL,21,Fahead."
